def palindrome_of_length_n(s):
    s = s.lower()
    s = ''.join(c for c in s if c.isalpha())
    palindromes = set()

    for i in range(len(s) - 317):
        substring = s[i:i+318]
        if substring == substring[::-1]:
            palindromes.add(substring)
    
    return palindromes
